metadata.name: Stay
metadata.description:
I will
Look for you
In every lifetime,
Until we finally stay

*************************
This image is a vision of feeling the presence of a lost loved one and the profound emotion of love which can be a saving grace.

**************************

This image was taken in Yosemite National park this last winter. It was 9° F. outside at the time of this shoot and was just a perfect setting for this image.

Image size : 4913 × 6141
